{"article_id":"86Makg7lBtvoyEjp","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Former federal prosecutor Lori Lightfoot took home the victory in Chicago 's mayoral race on Tuesday ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"making her the city 's first African American female mayor ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"the Associated Press projected .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Interested in 2020 Elections ?","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Add 2020 Elections as an interest","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"to stay up to date on the latest 2020 Elections news , video , and analysis from .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Add Interest","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"She had 74 % of the vote","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"with 66 % of the precincts reporting as of 9:30 p.m. Tuesday .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"The 56-year-old political newcomer defeated Cook County Board President Toni Preckwinkle , a 72-year-old former school teacher with nearly two decades of experience in public office .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"The two Democrats took the lead in a crowded field of 14 candidates in the February general election","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"to succeed two-term Mayor Rahm Emanuel .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Emanuel was not seeking re-election .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Lightfoot ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"also slated to become the city 's first openly gay mayor ,","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"will be sworn in May 20 .","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"She campaigned on a promise","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"to be a voice for low-income and working-class people","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"if elected .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"She spoke about her enthusiasm a few hours","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"before the polls closed on Tuesday ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"`` it would be a very big deal to beat the machine . \"","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"`` This campaign has been an incredible journey .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"We started out as underdogs ,","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"but our message of change resonated across the city .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"And today we have the chance","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"to make history , ''","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"Lightfoot said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"`` The energy and enthusiasm across the city has been incredible today . ''","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"\" It would be a very big deal to beat the machine . \"","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"The energy and enthusiasm across the city has been incredible today .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"We have less than 4 hours left","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"until the polls close ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"so make sure to make your voice heard !","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"https : //t.co/Z8UPx0t5ip","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"# TeamLightfoot","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"# LightfootGOTV","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"pic.twitter.com/X0VCyunEXC","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"- Lori Lightfoot","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"( @ LightfootForChi )","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"April 2 , 2019","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"Lightfoot has also vowed to bring change from the political status quo","depth":3},{"id":43,"text":"and end corruption in the city .","depth":3},{"id":44,"text":"`` What we have heard from people is that they are really , really sick and tired of the same old , same old","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"and want to break away from the past","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"and I think","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"that they view me as a change candidate ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"so I 'm excited about that , ''","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"Lightfoot told reporters outside of the polling station in the 35th Ward","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"where she lives .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"`` This has been the most wondrous journey of my life .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"There 's no question about it .","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"You try to plot the course . ''","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":107,"left":95,"right":106,"rela